{"tid":599651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友咁樣可以點做...","createTime":"2018-03-20T15:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T15:57:06.000Z","uid":177360,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4373c1798d065687aa5f1042e19afeb840d465eb","tid":599651,"uid":177360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T15:14:47.000Z","msg":"我有個fd，一直都係一個極度睇樣而且好快就會鍾意第二個既人。佢一直都係咁，半個月前，佢同一個幾靚既女仔一齊，佢當時話會愛佢一生一世。但冇幾耐之前，有一個幾可愛既女仔因爲係ig話當佢係男神，所以我個fd就變左鍾意佢，仲同本來個女仔分左手，走去同當佢男神個女仔一齊。我地成班fd都話佢賤格，咁佢就開始諗自己有幾賤，但係佢自己都好迷惘，唔知點算，我試過同佢傾過好多，但佢都唔明。我當佢兄弟，見佢咁難過，自己都唔係幾好受<br />\n想請教各位巴絲，應該點樣講佢先會明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：第一次開post</span>"},{"pid":"a368febd531c8a4f12cff95a1ae8469b146464bd","tid":599651,"uid":129453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T15:17:56.000Z","msg":"你朋友可以做既就係以後唔好拍拖 唔好出黎害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb059a8971c326c9d3d65255a114fa262f9960ab","tid":599651,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T15:20:36.000Z","msg":"你拎你碌鳩屌佢屎眼，屌到佢明為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91293e7ccc3a2a7fc38f8508d30efd47bd83e51","tid":599651,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/232321_7fa0938326170ed13af0d337e0740560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F232321_7fa0938326170ed13af0d337e0740560.jpg&h=0f6cf63d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d67fab3ba72cc3c0561fc08d79522642fdb9d3d5","tid":599651,"uid":177360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma